    "body":  "We are replacing the static image tag with an interactive 360 view.\n\n**Objective**: \nModify `MapUI.tsx` to use the `google.maps.StreetViewPanorama` component instead of the static image API. The current view is just a flat picture. To wow the judges, we want the user to be able to drag, pan, and explore the street view 360 degrees when they click on an agent.\n\n**Steps**:\n1. Check the official `@vis.gl/react-google-maps` documentation for their StreetView integration.\n2. Ensure you use the specific Lat/Lng of the `selectedAgent`.\n3. Add a smooth fade-in animation.",
